<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<%- include('partials/head') %>
<body class="container mt-5">
    <%- include('partials/header') %>
    <h1 class="mb-4"><%= title %></h1>

    <div class="mt-3">
        <p>Aşağıdaki tabloda Türkçe harfler, bunlara karşılık gelen Braille sembolleri ve nokta numaraları listelenmiştir.</p>
        
        <table class="table table-striped mt-3" aria-label="Braille Harfleri Tablosu">
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th scope="col">Harf</th>
                    <th scope="col">Braille Sembolü</th>
                    <th scope="col">Noktalar</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <% for (const key in charMap) { %>
                    <% if (charMap.hasOwnProperty(key)) { %>
                        <tr>
                            <td><%= charMap[key].character %></td>
                            <td class="braille-text" style="font-size: 1.5em;"><%= charMap[key].character %></td>
                            <td><%= charMap[key].dots.replace(/_/g, '-') %></td>
                        </tr>
                    <% } %>
                <% } %>
            </tbody>
        </table>
    </div>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
